item.title: About
item.description: My name is Nhat Dao and I love Computer Science and Mathematics. I work on projects and attend hackathons . In my freetime, I am generally found trying out new programming languages or jamming with my guitar and my keyboard. I am currently in my senior year at UT Arlington. Beside school, I’m also a web manager and mentor at Mobi . My recent resume is here .
